text: Katherine LaNasa (born December 1, 1966 in New Orleans, Louisiana) is an American movie and TV actress and dancer. She has acted in many television programs and movies.Katherine La Nasa LaNasa was married to actors Dennis Hopper, French Stewart and Grant Show. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:American television actors Category:American movie actors Category:Actors from Louisiana
